of a degrading solid. Based on these\nnumerical examples, we also discuss how plastic zones spread because of\nmaterial degradation. To illustrate how the proposed computational framework\nperforms, we report various performance metrics such as optimization iterations\nand time-to-solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2020 21:10:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-16"}
