er conditions, and power allocations on the performances of the CF- and\nUC-mMIMO networks are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2020 22:56:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2020 10:50:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 Mar 2021 10:37:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
